webfs

webfs is a basic HTTP based web server for getting, creating, editing, and deleting files.

It is meant as an simpler alternative to more complex protocols such as WebDAV.

Usage webfs [-b <bind address> -d <data directory> -v]
-b Specify the IP address and port to listen on
-d Specify the data directory to work in
Default is to listen on 127.0.0.1:8080 and work in the current directory